[[Image:Shang_Mac.jpeg|thumb|right|Shangri-La Mactan Island Resort & Spa]]
'''Shangri-La's Mactan Island Resort & Spa''' is a resort hotel owned by Shangri-La Hotels and Resorts located at the island of [[Mactan]], [[Cebu]]. It was once the [[Philippines]]' largest<ref>{{cite news |title=  A shangri-la at Shangri-La Mactan Island Resort |url=http://www.cebuprovince.com/articles.php?article_id=12 |publisher= [[The Philippine Star]] | first=Honey Jarque |last= Loop |date= August 21, 2005}}</ref>  and most exclusive deluxe resort, equipped with 546 guest rooms & suites.

